 witness to faith in prayer and to bear witness to faith in times of need. Bearing witness in prayer is to say, \u201cGreetings are for Allah, as are prayers and pure things.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35540,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/04\/jisr-jahannam\/","url_meta":{"origin":32675,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sirat: The Prophets pass over the bridge of Hell","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI will be the first to cross the bridge over Hell. The supplication of the Messengers on that day will be: O Allah, keep us safe! O Allah, keep us safe! There will be hooks on the sides\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17194,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/15\/dua-door-of-rahmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32675,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Door of mercy for those who supplicate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever among you has the door of supplication opened for him, the door of mercy is opened for him as well. Allah is not asked for anything more beloved to Him than to be asked for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33020,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/prophets-dua-after-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":32675,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet\u2019s supplication after finishing prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mughirah ibn Shu\u2019bah reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, finished the prayer and invoked peace, he would say, \u201cThere is no God but Allah, alone without partner. To him belongs the dominion, all praise, and he has power over all things. O Allah, none\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33174,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/11\/prophet-sacrifices-eid-al-adha\/","url_meta":{"origin":32675,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Adha: The Prophet sacrifices an animal on Eid al-Adha","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: I was present with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, on Eid al-Adha at the place of prayer. When the Prophet finished his sermon, he came down from his pulpit and a ram was brought to him. The Prophet slaughtered it with his own\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10878,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/02\/salat-qiyam-al-layl-near\/","url_meta":{"origin":32675,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tahajjud: Servants nearest to Allah pray at night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn 'Abasah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe closest the servant is to the Lord is during the last depth of the night. If you can be among those who remember Allah in this moment, then do so.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3579\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32675","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=32675"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32675\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=32675"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=32675"},{"taxonomy":"po